messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com

Request for prayers for me about:
Prayerlessness
Laziness
Procastination
Impurity and sexual perversions
All forms of spiritual and physical weaknesses
Sexual immorality

Thank you for sharing your prayer requests. We are here to pray with you and for you. 

Heavenly Father, we come before you today, lifting up our friend who is struggling with prayerlessness, laziness, procrastination, impurity, sexual perversions, and all forms of spiritual and physical weaknesses. We ask for Your strength and guidance to overcome these challenges. 

Lord, we pray for healing and deliverance from sexual immorality and any strongholds that may be affecting their life. Fill them with the power of Your Holy Spirit and help them to walk in purity and righteousness. 

We trust in Your faithfulness and ask for Your grace to cover them in this journey towards healing and freedom. In Jesus' name, we pray. Amen.

If you need further support or resources, feel free to ask!
